    <title>github+hexo简明安装教程</title>
    <link href="https://wolf123455.github.io/posts/36778.html"/>
    <id>https://wolf123455.github.io/posts/36778.html</id>
    <published>2021-05-09T09:34:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-22T05:29:02.894Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一、<strong>本地部署</strong><br>git <a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com</a><br>node.js <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">https://nodejs.org/en/</a><br>官方下载并一路默认安装<br>打开CMD命令行</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre class=" language-hljs plaintext"><code class="language-hljs plaintext">npm install -g hexo-cli<br>hexo init d:\my blog\hexo<br>d:<br>cd blog\hexo<br>hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><strong># 命令详情参考官方文档：</strong><br><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands.html">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands.html</a></p><p><strong>正常的话，此时已可以通过浏览器访问“localhost:4000”打开本地搭建的网页了<br>（hexo s 这个窗口不能关闭）</strong></p><p>小技巧：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre class=" language-hljs plaintext"><code class="language-hljs plaintext">hexo g -w<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre class=" language-hljs plaintext"><code class="language-hljs plaintext">hexo s -s<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>同时运行这2条命令，可实现本地网站内容更改后的实时更新。</p><p><strong>二、发布至Github</strong></p><p>1、注册Github</p><p>2、相关配置</p><ul><li>打开CMD命令行：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre class=" language-hljs plaintext"><code class="language-hljs plaintext">git config --global user.name "Github用户名" <br>git config --global user.email "Github注册邮箱"<br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "Github注册邮箱"<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><ul><li><p>**打开”.ssh”目录下的“id_rsa.pub”,全选复制。</p><p>去Github网站添加密钥（粘贴刚才复制的内容）。**</p><p>更改网站配置文件的如下部分：</p></li></ul><blockquote><p>deploy:    type: git    repo: 仓库地址.git</p></blockquote><p><em>CMD命令行进入本地网站主目录：</em></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre class=" language-hljs plaintext"><code class="language-hljs plaintext">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>3、<strong>上传网站</strong></p><ul><li> CMD进入本地网站主目录：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre class=" language-hljs plaintext"><code class="language-hljs plaintext">hexo clean<br>hexo g<br>hexo d<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><em>至此一切顺利的话，访问Github域名即可看到生成的网站了。</em></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
